    "   at 1536-d overfits with ~500 training samples and loses ~6 RMSE vs h alone.\n",
    "   Individual `gamma(k)` probes trail `h_past` by 2-3 RMSE. The predictor's\n",
    "   per-horizon output adds little for *regression*; its value is in\n",
    "   *event-specific queries* (Phase 4 direction, still weak here).\n",
