    "   Applying SIGReg to `h_past` drives PC1 to 0.22 (near-isotropic) but *erases\n",
    "   the RUL gradient* (+7 RMSE). Applying it to `gamma(k)` keeps h_past less\n",
    "   isotropic (PC1=0.43) but *preserves* downstream usefulness (15.38 test RMSE,\n",
    "   matching Phase 2 h_past). Curriculum successfully removes the target network\n",
